                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">star</span>
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined">star</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 italic">"I had a flat tire in my driveway and they came out same-day to replace it. Lifesavers!"</p>
                    <div class="font-bold text-brand-dark">- Jennifer L., Hoffman Estates</div>
                </div>

                <!-- Review 6 -->
