                    </div>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 italic">"Great communication from start to finish. The online booking was super easy to use."</p>
                    <div class="font-bold text-brand-dark">- David K., Barrington Hills</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center mt-20">
                <a href="/new-tires-installed" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition-all duration-200 bg-brand-dark rounded-full hover:bg-brand-light hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/20 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Experience It Yourself
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
